1. Moj *zamisao* je da putujem svetom. (My idea is to travel the world.)
2. Ona ima neobičnu *zamisao* o tome kako bi trebalo da izgleda njen dom. (She has an unusual idea about how her home should look like.)
3. Glavna *zamisao* ove knjige je da promoviše zdrav način života. (The main idea of this book is to promote a healthy lifestyle.)
4. Njegova *zamisao* je bila da postane doktor. (His idea was to become a doctor.)
5. Kako ti se čini moja *zamisao* za poklon za mamu? (What do you think about my idea for a gift for mom?)
6. *Zamisao* o ovoj izložbi je da predstavi radove savremenih umetnika. (The idea behind this exhibition is to showcase the works of contemporary artists.)
7. Njihova *zamisao* je bila da osnuju sopstveni biznis. (Their idea was to start their own business.)
8. Imamo *zamisao* da organizujemo humanitarnu akciju. (We have an idea to organize a charity event.)
9. Autorova *zamisao* je bila da knjiga bude zabavna za čitanje. (The author's idea was for the book to be entertaining to read.)
10. Njena *zamisao* je bila da se preseli u drugi grad. (Her idea was to move to another city.)